{"tid":1824304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡少芬張晉   慶祝鏈婚放閃","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T10:35:17.000Z","uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7127a55d6c88566589ea705094074443c04fb53d","tid":1824304,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"張晉與太太蔡少芬於2008年結婚，婚後兩人育有3子女，包括大女楚兒、二女信兒及細仔樂兒，夫妻二人恩愛如昔。轉眼間，兩人已結婚12年，張晉在微博分享片段放閃，片中的他伸手拖住正往前走的蔡少芬，並將太太擁入懷，畫面甜蜜溫馨。張晉留言︰「結婚紀念日，十二年風雨同路，今天扔下孩子，單獨請你吃晚餐。 對邊個好？對Ada唔好咩？」<br />\n<br />\n蔡少芬轉發片段，並向老公發表愛的宣言，她說：「十二年：鏈婚，像鐵鏈一樣，交織連鎖，永不分離。愛你啊張生！就好似人地王晶咁癡心情長劍咁，可以樣樣野都為晒邱淑貞去做。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4fLrLkS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4fLrLkS.jpg&h=5bec67c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d6d567f01fb21f7f8a931e235636babfdafeb70","tid":1824304,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxXd9NK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxXd9NK.png&h=bf859bfd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJvy9NK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJvy9NK.jpg&h=526dcd35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b7814eafe9d3046ea3ef0bbcb69d66d28f7cd17","tid":1824304,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUydqin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUydqin.gif&h=30becf79&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}